H0.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of Apollo's twin sister. Artemis

H1.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of Apollo's twin sister. Athena

H2.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of Apollo's twin sister. Aphrodite

H3.text: In Greek mythology, what was the name of Apollo's twin sister. Aetole

A4.text: In one account, Artemis is born first and then proceeds to assist Leto in the birth of the second twin, Apollo.

A5.text: In Greek tradition, Artemis is the daughter of Zeus and Leto, and twin sister of Apollo.
